high_descs: Turn around to face the room and go left past the refrigerator, then turn to face the sink on the right.
Pick up the green apple from the left side of the sink.
Turn around and take the apple to the microwave behind you.
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it, and remove it.
Turn around to your left and go back to the sink.
Put the apple back in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, turn to the left, and go to the sink to your right.
Pick up the apple that is to the right of the fork.
Turn around to the microwave above the stove.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn around to the sink behind you.
Place the apple in the sink, to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the sink.

high_descs: Pick up the apple in the sink on the left.
Bring the apple to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Bring the apple to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink, to the left of the other apple.
anns.task_desc: Heat the left apple in the microwave.
